data.text: So I’m not sure if it’s a typo, but in 5/3/1 Forever, page 117, you’ll find the layout of the Black Army Jacket anchor template. It shows Squat day 1, Deadlift day 2, Squat day 3, and Deadlift day 4. Is that right? We just aren’t supposed to bench or OHP on the anchor?
